# Picasso widget .gitignore — reconfigured 2026-07-02
#
# NOTE: the repo-root .gitignore ALSO applies to this subtree and blanket-
# ignores media files (*.png, *.svg, ...). This file is the override layer
# for Picasso: any media/test-like file that BELONGS in git needs an explicit
# `!` negation in the "Tracked exceptions" section at the bottom, or `git add`
# will silently skip it (this bit us with the Hairline design mocks).

# --- OS / editor noise ---
.DS_Store
._*
Thumbs.db
*~
*.swp
*.swo

# --- IDE / agent scratch ---
.vscode/
.idea/
.claude/

# --- Dependencies ---
node_modules/

# --- Build outputs ---
dist/
build/
chunks/
coverage/
# generated entry-point artifacts at repo root (real builds land in dist/)
/iframe-main.js
/iframe-main.js.map
/iframe-main.css
/iframe-main.css.map
/widget.js
/widget.js.map
/iframe.html

# --- Environment / local config ---
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
dev.config.json

# --- Logs / temp / cache ---
logs/
*.log
*.tmp
tmp/
.cache/

# --- Scratch areas ---
Sandbox/
backups/

# --- Archives / deployment packages ---
*.zip
*.tar.gz

# --- Backup-file suffixes ---
*.bak
*.backup
*.old

# --- One-time session/deployment summaries ---
*_DEPLOYMENT_*.md
*_COMPLETE_*.md
SESSION_RESUME_PROMPT.md

# --- Legacy local IaC: real content exists on disk but is deliberately
#     untracked; live IaC is the repo-root infra/ per the deployment SOP ---
infrastructure/

# --- Local test harnesses & debug screenshots (scratch by default) ---
test-*.html
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.svg
*.ico
*.mp4
*.mov

# --- Tracked exceptions (the negation layer — add here when a file belongs in git) ---
# Hairline design bundle: canonical mocks are source-of-truth
!design/hairline/bundle/*.png
# Canonical local verification harness (referenced by HAIRLINE_WORKPLAN done-criteria)
!/test-dynamic.html
# Deployed staging smoke page
!public/test-staging.html
# In-source assets (icons, powered-by mark)
!src/assets/**
# Bundled MyRecruiter powered-by mark (Hairline footer, W6.3 F2) — served
# from the dist root alongside fonts; esbuild copies it at build time
!public/myrecruiter-mark.png
